538
00:36:34,430 --> 00:36:35,639
Itu ironis.

539
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:38,149
Yah... Tuanku, harap jangan salah menuduhku.

540
00:36:38,149 --> 00:36:40,269
Aku membangun jembatan itu demi kebaikan orang-orang di sini.

541
00:36:40,269 --> 00:36:42,590
Tidak ada niat lain.

542
00:36:45,770 --> 00:36:48,270
Tuanku, lihatlah.

